      <title>杰里·韦斯特在 NBA 总决赛第三场比赛前默哀一分钟</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/nba-finals-mavericks-celtics-jerry-west-ad9296b1813128a996f9760c4902a1a1</link>
